casebody.data:
MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2004-2122. State ex rel. White v. Preble Cty. Bd. of Commrs.

In Mandamus. On joint motion for issuance of an agreed writ of mandamus. Motion denied. Cause shall continue in mediation.

Lundberg Stratton, J., dissents and would grant the joint motion and issue the writ.
